		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.serve-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-neon), var(--tertiary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

